{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":580,"text":"Melati Wijsen: Bali -- island of gods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":5301,"text":"Isabel Wijsen: A green paradise."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9139,"text":"MW: Or ..."},{"time":10576,"text":"a paradise lost."},{"time":13075,"text":"Bali:"},{"time":14696,"text":"island of garbage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":17707,"text":"IW: In Bali,"},{"time":18883,"text":"we generate 680 cubic meters\nof plastic garbage a day."},{"time":25801,"text":"That's about a 14-story building."},{"time":29205,"text":"And when it comes to plastic bags,"},{"time":31450,"text":"less than five percent gets recycled."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34900,"text":"MW: We know that changes the image\nyou may have of our island."},{"time":38666,"text":"It changed ours, too,\nwhen we learned about it,"},{"time":41174,"text":"when we learned that almost all\nplastic bags in Bali end up in our drains"},{"time":45759,"text":"and then in our rivers"},{"time":47033,"text":"and then in our ocean."},{"time":48900,"text":"And those that don't even\nmake it to the ocean,"},{"time":51388,"text":"they're either burned or littered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54183,"text":"IW: So we decided\nto do something about it."},{"time":56812,"text":"And we've been working\nfor almost three years now"},{"time":59335,"text":"to try to say no to plastic bags\non our home island."},{"time":62711,"text":"And we have had\nsome significant successes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66835,"text":"MW: We are sisters,"},{"time":68891,"text":"and we go to the best school on earth:"},{"time":72061,"text":"Green School, Bali."},{"time":73610,"text":"Green School is not only different\nin the way that it is built out of bamboo,"},{"time":78257,"text":"but also in the way that it teaches."},{"time":80864,"text":"We are taught to become leaders of today,"},{"time":84518,"text":"something a normal textbook cannot match."}]},{"cues":[{"time":87813,"text":"IW: One day we had a lesson in class"},{"time":89858,"text":"where we learned about significant people,"},{"time":92595,"text":"like Nelson Mandela,"},{"time":94107,"text":"Lady Diana"},{"time":95282,"text":"and Mahatma Gandhi."},{"time":97244,"text":"Walking home that day,"},{"time":98425,"text":"we agreed that we also\nwanted to be significant."},{"time":102614,"text":"Why should we wait until we were grown up"},{"time":104675,"text":"to be significant?"},{"time":106420,"text":"We wanted to do something now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109135,"text":"MW: Sitting on the sofa that night,"},{"time":110859,"text":"we brainstormed and thought\nof all the issues facing Bali."},{"time":114332,"text":"And one thing that stood out\nto us the most"},{"time":116420,"text":"was the plastic garbage."},{"time":118536,"text":"But that is a huge problem."},{"time":121189,"text":"So we looked into what was\na realistic target for us kids:"},{"time":125589,"text":"plastic bags."},{"time":126844,"text":"And the idea was born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128983,"text":"IW: We started researching,"},{"time":130988,"text":"and let's just say, the more we learned,"},{"time":133952,"text":"there was nothing good about plastic bags."},{"time":137401,"text":"And you know what?"},{"time":138695,"text":"We don't even need them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141003,"text":"MW: We were really inspired\nby the efforts to say no to plastic bags"},{"time":144568,"text":"in many other places,"},{"time":146462,"text":"from Hawaii to Rwanda"},{"time":148468,"text":"and to severals cities\nlike Oakland and Dublin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151784,"text":"IW: And so the idea turned into the launch\nof \"Bye Bye Plastic Bags.\""},{"time":158658,"text":"MW: In the years\nthat we have been campaigning,"},{"time":160874,"text":"we have learned a lot."}]},{"cues":[{"time":163984,"text":"Lesson number one:"},{"time":166233,"text":"you cannot do it all by yourself."},{"time":168415,"text":"You need a big team of like-minded kids,"},{"time":170631,"text":"and so we formed\nthe Bye Bye Plastic Bags crew."},{"time":174459,"text":"The volunteer team includes\nchildren from all over the island,"},{"time":177598,"text":"from both international and local schools."},{"time":180505,"text":"And together with them,"},{"time":181680,"text":"we started a multi-layered approach,"},{"time":183454,"text":"based on an on- and off-line\nsignature petition,"},{"time":186774,"text":"educational and inspirational\npresentations at schools"},{"time":190234,"text":"and we raise general awareness\nat markets, festivals, beach clean-ups."},{"time":194743,"text":"And last but not least,"},{"time":195918,"text":"we distribute alternative bags,"},{"time":197988,"text":"bags like net bags,"},{"time":199736,"text":"recycled newspaper bags"},{"time":201082,"text":"or 100 percent organic material bags,"},{"time":203826,"text":"all made by local\ninitiatives on the island."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206898,"text":"IW: We run a pilot village,"},{"time":208316,"text":"home of 800 families."},{"time":210952,"text":"The village mayor was our first friend"},{"time":212799,"text":"and he loved our T-shirts, so that helped."},{"time":216077,"text":"We focused on making the customers aware,"},{"time":218769,"text":"because that's where the change\nneeds to happen."},{"time":222266,"text":"The village is already\ntwo-thirds along the way"},{"time":224487,"text":"of becoming plastic bag free."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227330,"text":"Our first attempts to get the government\nof Bali on board failed."},{"time":232696,"text":"So we thought,"},{"time":234391,"text":"\"Hmm ... a petition\nwith one million signatures."},{"time":238715,"text":"They can't ignore us, right?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":240732,"text":"MW: Right!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":242258,"text":"IW: But, who would have guessed"},{"time":244117,"text":"one million signatures is, like,\na thousand times a thousand?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248303,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250270,"text":"We got stuck --"},{"time":252747,"text":"till we learned lesson number two:"},{"time":255507,"text":"think outside the box."},{"time":257808,"text":"Someone mentioned"},{"time":258983,"text":"that the Bali airport handles\n16 million arrivals and departures a year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266294,"text":"MW: But how do we get into the airport?"},{"time":269993,"text":"And here comes lesson number three:"},{"time":272236,"text":"persistence."},{"time":274141,"text":"Off we headed to the airport."},{"time":275792,"text":"We got past the janitor."},{"time":277819,"text":"And then it was his boss's boss,"},{"time":279729,"text":"and then the assistant office manager,"},{"time":282014,"text":"and then the office manager,"},{"time":283423,"text":"and then ..."},{"time":284618,"text":"we got shuffled down\ntwo levels and thought,"},{"time":286789,"text":"well, here comes the janitor again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289537,"text":"And after several days knocking on doors"},{"time":291609,"text":"and just being kids on a mission,"},{"time":293949,"text":"we finally got to the commercial\nmanager of Bali airports."},{"time":298368,"text":"And we gave him the \"Bali of plastic bags\"\nspeech, and being a very nice man,"},{"time":302305,"text":"he said, [imitating the man's voice]\n\"I cannot believe what I'm about say,"},{"time":306027,"text":"but I'm going to give authorization"},{"time":308294,"text":"to collect signatures\nbehind customs and immigrations.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":311275,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":312643,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":316962,"text":"IW: In our first hour and a half there,"},{"time":318930,"text":"we got almost 1,000 signatures."},{"time":321954,"text":"How cool is that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":324340,"text":"Lesson number four:"},{"time":325875,"text":"you need champions\nat all levels of society,"},{"time":329486,"text":"from students to commercial\nmanagers to famous people."},{"time":334097,"text":"And thanks to the attraction\nof Green School,"},{"time":336233,"text":"we had access to a steady\nstream of celebrities."},{"time":339937,"text":"Ban Ki Moon taught us"},{"time":341160,"text":"that Secretary-Generals\nof the United Nations"},{"time":344545,"text":"don't sign petitions --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":346220,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347245,"text":"even if kids ask nicely."},{"time":349106,"text":"But he promised to spread the word,"},{"time":350815,"text":"and now we work closely\nwith the United Nations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353701,"text":"MW: Jane Goodall taught us\nthe power of a people's network."},{"time":357055,"text":"She started with just one\nRoots &amp; Shoots group"},{"time":360119,"text":"and now she has 4,000 groups\naround the world."},{"time":363434,"text":"We are one of them."},{"time":364631,"text":"She's a real inspiration."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366731,"text":"If you're a fellow Rotarian,"},{"time":368507,"text":"nice to meet you."},{"time":369821,"text":"We're Interactors,"},{"time":370996,"text":"the youngest department\nof Rotary International."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374573,"text":"IW: But we have also learned\nmuch about patience,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377840,"text":"MW: how to deal with frustrations,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":380121,"text":"IW: leadership,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":381296,"text":"MW: teamwork,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382489,"text":"IW: friendship,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":383664,"text":"MW: we learned more\nabout the Balinese and their culture"}]},{"cues":[{"time":386347,"text":"IW: and we learned\nabout the importance of commitment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390106,"text":"MW: It's not always easy."},{"time":391864,"text":"Sometimes it does get\na little bit hard to walk your talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":395830,"text":"IW: But last year, we did exactly that."},{"time":398663,"text":"We went to India to give a talk,"},{"time":400290,"text":"and our parents took us to visit"},{"time":401869,"text":"the former private house\nof Mahatma Gandhi."},{"time":405216,"text":"We learned about the power\nof hunger strikes"},{"time":407494,"text":"he did to reach his goals."},{"time":409329,"text":"Yes, by the end of the tour,"},{"time":411351,"text":"when we met our parents again,"},{"time":413026,"text":"we both made a decision and said,"},{"time":414716,"text":"\"We're going on a hunger strike!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":416496,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":417521,"text":"MW: And you can probably\nimagine their faces."},{"time":420444,"text":"It took a lot of convincing,"},{"time":422746,"text":"and not only to our parents"},{"time":424502,"text":"but to our friends\nand to our teachers as well."},{"time":427561,"text":"Isabel and I were serious\nabout doing this."},{"time":430556,"text":"So we met with a nutritionist,"},{"time":432189,"text":"and we came up with a compromise"},{"time":434053,"text":"of not eating from sunrise\nto sunset every day"},{"time":438342,"text":"until the governor of Bali\nwould agree to meet with us"},{"time":440971,"text":"to talk about how to stop\nplastic bags on Bali."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445118,"text":"IW: Our \"mogak makan,\"\nas it is called in Bahasa Indonesia,"},{"time":449162,"text":"started."},{"time":450337,"text":"We used social media to support our goal"},{"time":452350,"text":"and already on day two,"},{"time":454141,"text":"police started to come\nto our home and school."},{"time":456724,"text":"What were these two girls doing?"},{"time":459466,"text":"We knew we weren't making\nthe governor look his best"},{"time":462000,"text":"by doing this food strike --"},{"time":463905,"text":"we could have gone to jail."},{"time":465768,"text":"But, hey, it worked."},{"time":467721,"text":"Twenty-four hours later,"},{"time":468971,"text":"we were picked up from school"},{"time":470407,"text":"and escorted to the office\nof the governor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":473283,"text":"MW: And there he was --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":474820,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":477053,"text":"waiting for us to meet and speak,"},{"time":479007,"text":"being all supportive\nand thankful for our willingness"},{"time":481581,"text":"to care for the beauty\nand the environment of Bali."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484812,"text":"He signed a promise"},{"time":485987,"text":"to help the people of Bali\nsay no to plastic bags."},{"time":488762,"text":"And we are now friends,"},{"time":489940,"text":"and on a regular basis,"},{"time":491360,"text":"we remind him and his team\nof the promises he has made."},{"time":495372,"text":"And indeed,"},{"time":496547,"text":"recently he stated and committed"},{"time":498477,"text":"that Bali will be\nplastic bag free by 2018."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503144,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":511498,"text":"IW: Also, at the International Airport\nof Bali, one of our supporters"},{"time":516139,"text":"is planning to start\na plastic bag-free policy by 2016."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521186,"text":"MW: Stop handing out free plastic bags"},{"time":523197,"text":"and bring in your own reusable bag"},{"time":524917,"text":"is our next message to change\nthat mindset of the public."}]},{"cues":[{"time":529405,"text":"IW: Our short-term campaign,"},{"time":531126,"text":"\"One Island / One Voice,\""},{"time":532582,"text":"is all about this."},{"time":534040,"text":"We check and recognize\nthe shops and restaurants"},{"time":536743,"text":"that have declared themselves\na plastic bag-free zone,"},{"time":539610,"text":"and we put this sticker at their entrance"},{"time":542007,"text":"and publish their names on social media"},{"time":544349,"text":"and some important magazines on Bali."},{"time":546829,"text":"And conversely,"},{"time":548004,"text":"that highlights those\nwho do not have the sticker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550853,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":552731,"text":"MW: So, why are we actually\ntelling you all of this?"},{"time":556673,"text":"Well, partly, it is because we are proud"},{"time":558615,"text":"of the results that,\ntogether with our team,"},{"time":560710,"text":"we have been able to reach."},{"time":562469,"text":"But also because along the way,"},{"time":564581,"text":"we have learned that kids can do things."},{"time":567445,"text":"We can make things happen."},{"time":569891,"text":"Isabel and I were only 10 and 12 years old"},{"time":572342,"text":"when we started this."},{"time":573925,"text":"We never had a business plan,"},{"time":576002,"text":"nor a fixed strategy,"},{"time":577250,"text":"nor any hidden agendas --"},{"time":579193,"text":"just the idea in front of us"},{"time":581657,"text":"and a group of friends working with us."},{"time":584195,"text":"All we wanted to do\nwas stop those plastic bags"},{"time":586465,"text":"from wrapping and suffocating\nour beautiful home."},{"time":589933,"text":"Kids have a boundless energy"},{"time":591665,"text":"and a motivation to be the change\nthe world needs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596454,"text":"IW: So to all the kids of this beautiful\nbut challenging world:"},{"time":601690,"text":"go for it!"},{"time":602868,"text":"Make that difference."},{"time":605057,"text":"We're not telling you\nit's going to be easy."},{"time":607500,"text":"We're telling you\nit's going to be worth it."},{"time":610221,"text":"Us kids may only be 25 percent\nof the world's population,"},{"time":614616,"text":"but we are 100 percent of the future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":619050,"text":"MW: We still have a lot of work to do,"},{"time":621730,"text":"but know that we still not stop"},{"time":623419,"text":"until the first question asked\nwhen arriving at the Bali airports will be"}]},{"cues":[{"time":628682,"text":"Both: \"Welcome to Bali,"},{"time":630040,"text":"do you have nay plastic bags to declare?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":632231,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":633668,"text":"Om shanti shanti shanti om."}]},{"cues":[{"time":636428,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637603,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}